item.description: We will be meeting at noon at DaLat on Park Avenue in Worcester. This will leave everyone with plenty of time to get settled in for the Patriot's victory later on!! Feel free to call me with any questions.. 508-410-3172. This is also a BYOB place, so if you want to bring some beer or wine.. feel free. It's a family friendly event though so save the hard stuff for the game lol. See you all there.. hope you didn't give up on me/the group.
item.how_to_find_us: You can't miss me! The white dude with the dreads..
item.why: It's tasty vietnamese food at a good price.
item.name: We're back in action this Sunday!!
